WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.680
People were wondering about

00:00:03.060 --> 00:00:06.000
prayer cues and things like that. They

00:00:04.680 --> 00:00:07.140
want to know some more things, so I'm

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:09.960
going to give you a couple right here.

00:00:07.140 --> 00:00:11.700
Okay, in Ephesians it talks about how we

00:00:09.960 --> 00:00:14.460
wrestle not against flesh and blood, but

00:00:11.700 --> 00:00:16.020
against principalities and powers, and

00:00:14.460 --> 00:00:18.539
there's a lot more to the verse. But for

00:00:16.020 --> 00:00:22.100
time's sake, there you go. It's Ephesians 4:16,

00:00:18.539 --> 00:00:26.400
I believe, somewhere around there.

00:00:22.100 --> 00:00:29.640
You cannot pray against somebody's will.

00:00:26.400 --> 00:00:32.159
Okay, like say you go to work and

00:00:29.640 --> 00:00:35.040
your boss is really mean to you. Maybe

00:00:32.159 --> 00:00:38.099
you're a teenager right now and you're

00:00:35.040 --> 00:00:40.260
watching me, and you are in a verbally abusive

00:00:38.100 --> 00:00:42.840
relationship with your parents.

00:00:40.260 --> 00:00:46.920
When you are being assaulted like that,

00:00:42.840 --> 00:00:51.300
it is a demonic presence behind it, and

00:00:46.920 --> 00:00:53.579
so you take authority over the devil.

00:00:51.300 --> 00:00:56.038
This is how I would do it. I had a boss

00:00:53.579 --> 00:00:59.340
that was not very nice to me, and he

00:00:56.039 --> 00:01:02.579
treated me pretty poorly. So every day I

00:00:59.340 --> 00:01:05.880
would drive to work and say, 'I bind the

00:01:02.579 --> 00:01:10.260
maneuvering of any demonic spirits in so-and-so,

00:01:05.880 --> 00:01:13.740
and you will not torment me in

00:01:10.260 --> 00:01:16.200
any way today at all. I take authority

00:01:13.740 --> 00:01:20.419
over the spirits that maneuver inside of

00:01:16.200 --> 00:01:23.880
him, and I command them to stop right now.

00:01:20.420 --> 00:01:26.640
You have no right, no power, no authority,

00:01:23.880 --> 00:01:29.399
and I bind you up, and you are not able

00:01:26.640 --> 00:01:31.460
to maneuver and torment in any way in the

00:01:29.400 --> 00:01:34.799
name of Jesus.'Concerning

00:01:31.460 --> 00:01:37.500
abuse, I bind the devils that

00:01:34.799 --> 00:01:41.280
are tormenting my husband or my wife.

00:01:37.500 --> 00:01:43.500
I bind that devil in the name of Jesus. I

00:01:41.280 --> 00:01:46.320
command you to cease and desist in your

00:01:43.500 --> 00:01:49.680
maneuvering, and I command you to stop it

00:01:46.320 --> 00:01:53.220
right now. You will not

00:01:49.680 --> 00:01:54.659
maneuver in them anymore. I command you

00:01:53.220 --> 00:01:58.979
to stop this,

00:01:54.659 --> 00:02:01.439
and I call peace to the spouse, or

00:01:58.979 --> 00:02:04.920
whoever, in the name of Jesus. I call

00:02:01.439 --> 00:02:07.679
peace over them, and that's how I pray. I

00:02:04.920 --> 00:02:10.619
don't bind them. You can't bind them

00:02:07.680 --> 00:02:11.940
because they have free will, okay? And you

00:02:10.619 --> 00:02:13.440
get into some kind of witchcraft

00:02:11.940 --> 00:02:15.840
sometimes when you start doing that,

00:02:13.440 --> 00:02:17.340
praying over their emotions. It's like

00:02:15.840 --> 00:02:18.780
when I'm trying to

00:02:17.340 --> 00:02:21.720
sell something in my business or

00:02:18.780 --> 00:02:24.239
whatever. I don't pray over that person,

00:02:21.720 --> 00:02:29.040
'Father, I thank you that you cause them

00:02:24.239 --> 00:02:32.520
to buy my product.'Okay? I say

00:02:29.040 --> 00:02:36.179
this: 'Father, I thank you that my product

00:02:32.520 --> 00:02:39.420
stands out. Father, I thank you that my

00:02:36.180 --> 00:02:42.239
product is desirable, that people want

00:02:39.420 --> 00:02:44.220
what I'm selling. I thank you, Father, that

00:02:42.239 --> 00:02:46.140
I am blessed in the city and the field,

00:02:44.220 --> 00:02:49.620
coming in and going out, according to

00:02:46.140 --> 00:02:52.079
Deuteronomy 28. And Father, I thank you

00:02:49.620 --> 00:02:54.840
that when people see my

00:02:52.080 --> 00:02:57.420
stuff and what I'm selling today,

00:02:54.840 --> 00:02:59.940
they want what I have because it stands out.'But

00:02:57.420 --> 00:03:03.420
I don't pray over their

00:02:59.940 --> 00:03:04.980
emotions manipulating them. You

00:03:03.420 --> 00:03:06.660
don't manipulate people in the

00:03:04.980 --> 00:03:09.060
spirit realm. It's part of

00:03:06.660 --> 00:03:10.859
witchcraft, okay? You don't do that. You

00:03:09.060 --> 00:03:12.659
just pray over your stuff. You pray,

00:03:10.860 --> 00:03:15.180
'Father, my stuff is going to stand out.

00:03:12.659 --> 00:03:18.420
Thank you, Lord.'And Father, when it comes

00:03:15.180 --> 00:03:20.819
to your unsaved loved ones,

00:03:18.420 --> 00:03:22.799
if they're out drinking or partying or

00:03:20.819 --> 00:03:26.399
being promiscuous or whatever:

00:03:22.800 --> 00:03:28.739
'Father, I thank you for Johnny, or whoever. I

00:03:26.400 --> 00:03:30.659
thank you, Father, that he is saved.

00:03:28.739 --> 00:03:32.819
Father, I thank you, Lord, right now that you send

00:03:30.659 --> 00:03:35.340
laborers across his

00:03:32.819 --> 00:03:38.579
path, whether they're at Walmart or wherever.

00:03:35.340 --> 00:03:40.920
Let somebody come across his

00:03:38.580 --> 00:03:43.620
path and witness to him today.

00:03:40.920 --> 00:03:46.920
Now, Father, I thank you. I bind the spirit

00:03:43.620 --> 00:03:50.879
of addiction off of his life.

00:03:46.920 --> 00:03:53.819
I take authority over alcoholism. I take

00:03:50.879 --> 00:03:56.940
authority over drug addiction.'He may be

00:03:53.819 --> 00:04:00.119
strung out on meth or

00:03:56.940 --> 00:04:02.280
prescription pills. 'I bind the spirit of

00:04:00.120 --> 00:04:05.040
addiction off of his life right now in

00:04:02.280 --> 00:04:07.739
the name of Jesus. I call that spirit to

00:04:05.040 --> 00:04:10.920
cease and desist in its maneuvering in

00:04:07.739 --> 00:04:13.980
his life. I command it to bow its knee.

00:04:10.920 --> 00:04:16.978
You have no authority to torment him

00:04:13.980 --> 00:04:19.738
anymore. You're a foul devil, and I

00:04:16.978 --> 00:04:22.560
command you to release him right now in

00:04:19.738 --> 00:04:25.620
the name of Jesus. If they're wayward now,

00:04:22.560 --> 00:04:28.500
angels, I send you out. Go and bring

00:04:25.620 --> 00:04:30.780
Johnny, or whoever, home to me. Bring them

00:04:28.500 --> 00:04:33.000
home. Father, I thank you, Holy Spirit,

00:04:30.780 --> 00:04:35.460
you're working on their hearts right now.

00:04:33.000 --> 00:04:38.639
I call them to have a heart that's

00:04:35.460 --> 00:04:40.620
pliable. Oh God, I minister to them right now.'There

00:04:38.639 --> 00:04:41.940
it goes, it started hitting me

00:04:40.620 --> 00:04:44.940
in the intercession.

00:04:41.940 --> 00:04:44.940
Hallelujah.

00:04:46.080 --> 00:04:48.740
'Okay,

00:04:48.780 --> 00:04:52.500
I pray over their heart right now in the

00:04:50.759 --> 00:04:54.540
name of Jesus.

00:04:52.500 --> 00:04:56.400
Call him in,

00:04:54.540 --> 00:04:58.500
bring them in. Lord,

00:04:56.400 --> 00:04:59.340
I thank you. Lord, we're not giving up on

00:04:58.500 --> 00:05:01.139
them.

00:04:59.340 --> 00:05:03.780
Father, I thank you, Lord, that you're

