00:24:07.620 --> 00:24:13.620
to get people free. So Father, I thank

00:24:11.280 --> 00:24:15.720
you right now in the name of Jesus. I'm

00:24:13.620 --> 00:24:19.379
going to do a blanket prayer for all the

00:24:15.720 --> 00:24:22.500
people that have asked for help, all the

00:24:19.380 --> 00:24:26.159
prayer needs, all the healings, and

00:24:22.500 --> 00:24:28.500
the people dying of a

00:24:26.159 --> 00:24:30.960
disease, or whose loved

00:24:28.500 --> 00:24:34.380
ones are far away from the Lord.

00:24:30.960 --> 00:24:37.080
Father, we thank you, Lord. You showed me

00:24:34.380 --> 00:24:38.940
in a vision today, Lord, little birds.

00:24:37.080 --> 00:24:41.699
I said, 'Father, they're like little

00:24:38.940 --> 00:24:43.980
birds chirping in a mama's nest, and

00:24:41.700 --> 00:24:45.960
they're asking for help, help, help, cheep, cheep, cheep.'I

00:24:43.980 --> 00:24:48.539
saw them in the Spirit,

00:24:45.960 --> 00:24:51.659
Lord, and I said, 'God, there are so many mouths

00:24:48.539 --> 00:24:53.280
to feed. I can't do it all, I don't

00:24:51.659 --> 00:24:54.240
know what you want me to do.'And you said

00:24:53.280 --> 00:24:57.178
to me,

00:24:54.240 --> 00:25:00.419
'It's my job, Brandon. The Holy Spirit will

00:24:57.179 --> 00:25:02.880
take care of this.'And I saw that big

00:25:00.419 --> 00:25:06.539
bird dump a whole bunch of worms on those

00:25:02.880 --> 00:25:08.520
little babies. Today I pray that for

00:25:06.539 --> 00:25:10.740
you. The Holy Spirit is going to meet

00:25:08.520 --> 00:25:13.799
every need you have, right where you're

00:25:10.740 --> 00:25:15.900
at. Jesus has got this for you. I call

00:25:13.799 --> 00:25:18.600
healing over your bodies. I call

00:25:15.900 --> 00:25:21.240
deliverance over you in Jesus'name. I

00:25:18.600 --> 00:25:23.280
call restoration over your marriages. You

00:25:21.240 --> 00:25:25.260
may be having marriage problems; I call

00:25:23.280 --> 00:25:27.720
restoration over your marriages in Jesus'name.

00:25:25.260 --> 00:25:30.480
I call blessing over your

00:25:27.720 --> 00:25:32.340
home in Jesus'name financially. I pray

00:25:30.480 --> 00:25:33.960
that the Lord will

00:25:32.340 --> 00:25:36.299
bless you and keep you, may His face

00:25:33.960 --> 00:25:38.400
shine upon you and be gracious to you,

00:25:36.299 --> 00:25:40.980
and give you peace. I call those

00:25:38.400 --> 00:25:43.500
blessings over your home in Jesus'name.

00:25:40.980 --> 00:25:46.080
We praise the Lord for everything

00:25:43.500 --> 00:25:49.440
He's already done and what He continues

00:25:46.080 --> 00:25:51.779
to do in your life in the name of Jesus.

00:25:49.440 --> 00:25:54.360
Put a smile on your face and a song in

00:25:51.779 --> 00:25:56.220
your heart. Jesus loves you, and I love

00:25:54.360 --> 00:25:58.620
you, and I'm so thankful that you're part

00:25:56.220 --> 00:26:01.100
of my family here. God bless you all.

00:25:58.620 --> 00:26:01.100
Bye-bye.

